c.Direct the accountable Officers of cash advances to immediately liquidate their cash advances as soon as the purpose of it has been served, or within the prescribed time as stated in COA Circular 97-002; and,
d.Issue a withholding order to the salary of the accountable officers that violates the aforementioned regulations, specifically Section 89 of PD 1445.

